    <string name="about_activity_title">About the APP</string>
    <string name="about_activity_title_paragraph_1">Resume</string>
    <string name="about_activity_text_1">This application\'s goal is to list all the repositories for each programming language from the Github API. Moreover, it is possible to view information about a specific repository, such as, a description, the repository\'s owner, a the number of stars and forks and all the pull requests currently active.</string>
